Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.71,0:08:39.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-够了  -威廉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}-That will be enough! -William.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.44,0:08:40.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}Out!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.15,0:08:43.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你刚才是怎么回事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}What was that about?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.57,0:08:47.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-你必须告诉我  -他杀了我最好的朋友\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}-You have to tell me. -He murdered my best friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.60,0:08:48.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.77,0:08:51.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的大学挚友  罗素·罗杰斯\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}My mate from college. Russell Rogers.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.41,0:08:54.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两年前  他开始怀疑罗哈斯家族\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}Two years ago, he got suspicious of the Rojases,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.40,0:08:57.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第二天  那个怪物就杀了他\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}and the next day, that monster killed him.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.07,0:09:00.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-至今没找到尸体  -那你怎么知道他死了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}- Never found the body. - Then how do you know he's dead?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.21,0:09:03.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这些都是专业杀手  不会留下证据的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}These are professional killers. They don't leave evidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.44,0:09:05.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有个朋友能帮忙调查这件事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}I have a friend that could help with this.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.17,0:09:06.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我根本不该告诉你这些\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}I should have never told you any of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.46,0:09:09.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在你越陷越深了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}Now look how involved you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.06,0:09:13.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我才叫你别插手\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}It's why I told you to stay away.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.05,0:09:17.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是情感的深渊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}It's an emotional abyss.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.99,0:09:22.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fn方正兰亭黑_GBK\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}峰脑堡  军事基地
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.46,0:09:31.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不许动  放下箱子\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}Hold it. Set the case down.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.90,0:09:33.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,转过身来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}Turn around.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.81,0:09:37.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,举起双手\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}Show me your hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.05,0:09:57.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,罗素·罗杰斯\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}Russell Rogers.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.04,0:10:01.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-我会调查他失踪的事  -谢谢你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}- I'll look into his disappearance. - Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.61,0:10:03.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你感觉如何\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}And how are you feeling?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.44,0:10:06.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,经历了马拉的这么多事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}With everything that happened with Mal...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.69,0:10:08.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还在消化整件事情\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}Well, I'm still processing it all.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.10,0:10:12.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但这让我更深地了解自己\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}But it gave me deeper knowledge about myself and...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.55,0:10:13.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和我的族人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}And my people.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.94,0:10:15.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我能从中学到东西\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}I can learn from that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.45,0:10:17.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么样  你还好吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}How about you? Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.53,0:10:19.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你经历了许多\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}You've been through a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.74,0:10:22.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你讨厌的记者原来是好人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}The reporter you hated turns out to be a good guy
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.21,0:10:25.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安德里亚·罗哈斯可能与多起凶杀案有关\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}and Andrea Rojas is potentially involved in murders.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.45,0:10:28.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  除了你和艾丽克斯我不能告诉任何人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}Yeah, I can't talk about this with anyone but you and Alex.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.10,0:10:30.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我对威廉发誓我会保密\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}I swore to William I'd keep it secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.35,0:10:31.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甚至不能告诉尼娅\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}Even from Nia.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.37,0:10:34.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但说实话  我心烦意乱\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}But honestly, I... I'm, I'm reeling.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.95,0:10:37.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我永远不会想到安德里亚是罪犯\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}I never would have thought Andrea was a criminal
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.41,0:10:40.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我之前还很确信威廉是坏人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}and I was convinced William was evil.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.89,0:10:42.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我对他们俩的看法怎么错得如此离谱\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}How could I have been so wrong about both of them?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.91,0:10:44.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在  到处都是黑曜石的科技\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}And now, with Obsidian tech everywhere,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.82,0:10:49.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所有人都陷在虚拟世界中\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}I mean, everyone's just in these make-believe worlds and...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.26,0:10:51.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如今很难搞清什么才是真的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}It's hard to know what's real anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.60,0:10:54.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只希望能更确定\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}I just want some certainty.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.69,0:10:58.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马拉法克的事给我的最大教训就是\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}You know, my biggest takeaway from what happened with Malefic,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.10,0:11:00.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当世界充满不确定性\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}is when the world is uncertain,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.99,0:11:03.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有一样东西坚如磐石\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}there's one thing that's rock solid.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.57,0:11:05.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是爱你的人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}It's the people who love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.52,0:11:10.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾丽克斯叫我回超查部\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}Alex needs me at the DEO.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.79,0:11:16.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人闯入峰脑堡\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}We had a break-in at Fort Summit.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.64,0:11:18.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托别告诉我是莱克斯的保险库\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}Please don't tell me it is Lex's vault.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.44,0:11:21.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正确  这就是袭击者\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}Indeed. And this is the assailant.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.80,0:11:23.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是威廉提到的那个人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}It is the same guy William talked about.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.36,0:11:24.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他偷了什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}What did he steal?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.71,0:11:27.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卢瑟先生称之为马拉松激光束\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}Mr. Luthor called it his Marathon Laser.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.00,0:11:30.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它能发射一道集中热能\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}It's able to launch a concentrated beam of heat
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.30,0:11:33.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最远能瞄准42千米外的目标\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}at a target up to 26.2 miles away.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.54,0:11:34.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是杀手的理想武器\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}It's an assassin's dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.88,0:11:36.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们有办法追踪它吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}Is there any way we can track it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.54,0:11:38.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们正在扫描武器\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}We are scanning for the weapon.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.16,0:11:40.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幸运的话  也能帮我们追踪到那人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}With any luck, that will lead us to the man as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.60,0:11:41.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,威廉说\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}William said
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.57,0:11:44.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘶吼是罗哈斯的杀手小队成员之一\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}Rip Roar was a part of the Rojases's team of operatives.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.99,0:11:47.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在他们在安德里亚的眼镜上线前一天\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}Now they're stealing one of Lex's weapons
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.82,0:11:50.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去偷莱克斯的武器\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}the day before the launch of Andrea's lenses?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.93,0:11:53.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,假如威廉·戴没怀疑错安德里亚·罗哈斯\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}If William Dey is right about Andrea Rojas,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.02,0:11:54.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两件事之间很可能有关联\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}there's a high probability of a connection.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.96,0:11:57.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但凯莉说虚拟现实设备的发布也是虚拟的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}But Kelly did say the VR launch is virtual.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.49,0:11:59.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以人们不会聚集在一处\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}So people aren't gonna be gathering in one place.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.57,0:12:01.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那这武器是用来做什么的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}So what use is that weapon then?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.01,0:12:02.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们肯定忽略了什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}We've gotta be missing something.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.50,0:12:04.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我再去审问窒息者\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}I'll take another run at Breathtaker.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.01,0:12:05.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  我们审问过了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}No, we tried that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.34,0:12:07.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算戴上求真者  也什么都问不出来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}Even with the Truth Seeker, she's got nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.32,0:12:09.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我或许有办法\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}I might have a solution.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.18,0:12:14.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们不是还抓到了另一个杀手吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}There is always the other assassin we caught.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.16,0:12:15.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁  奥康纳\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}What, O'Connor?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.48,0:12:16.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-她死了  -是的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}- She's dead. - Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.06,0:12:19.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但她的纹身还活着  有自主意识\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}But her tattoos are alive and sentient.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.82,0:12:21.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们不需要宿主吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}Wouldn't we need a host?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.53,0:12:22.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  需要\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}We would, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.05,0:12:26.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我醒着的时候来找我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}Approaching me while I'm still conscious.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.79,0:12:29.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真体贴\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}How thoughtful of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.73,0:12:31.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来我们对彼此的第一印象不太好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}It seems we have gotten off on the wrong foot.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.06,0:12:34.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我有个提议\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}So I have a proposition.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.46,0:12:38.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有能力在人们脑中植入想法\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}You have the ability to incept thoughts into people's minds.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.56,0:12:39.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想研究你的大脑\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}I want to study your brain,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.67,0:12:42.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以开发有相同能力的科技\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}so I can develop a technology that can do the same thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.08,0:12:44.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原谅我的疑心\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}Forgive my skepticism,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.58,0:12:47.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但上次有人对我的大脑感兴趣时\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}but last time someone showed interest in my brain,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.54,0:12:50.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高级议会将我流放到了幻影区\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}the High Council sent me to the Phantom Zone.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.53,0:12:52.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果不是因为我  你早就回到幻影区了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}You'd be back in the Phantom Zone if it wasn't for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.88,0:12:56.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然而  我们陷入了僵局\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}And yet, now we are at an impasse.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.74,0:13:02.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有什么好处\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}What's in it for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.05,0:13:04.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们俩目标一致\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}We both want the same thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.03,0:13:08.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都遭到最亲近之人的背叛\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}We were each betrayed by the people closest to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.03,0:13:11.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟我合作\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}Work with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.58,0:13:13.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我相信你有能力做大事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}I believe you've the ability to do great things.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.86,0:13:16.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想做大事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}I don't want to do great things.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.81,0:13:18.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要复仇\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}I want revenge.
