Dialogue: 0,0:25:07.39,0:25:10.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}索科罗卫星站
Dialogue: 0,0:25:15.24,0:25:16.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘶吼\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}Rip Roar.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:17.99,0:25:19.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道你是谁\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}I know who you are.
