Dialogue: 0,0:25:21.95,0:25:23.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你一无所知\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}You know nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:23.62,0:25:25.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并且无能为力\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}And you're out of your depth.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:38.09,0:25:39.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚丽克斯\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}Alex.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:39.68,0:25:40.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我需要荣恩\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}I need J'onn.
