Dialogue: 0,0:25:54.00,0:25:55.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我好多了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}I'm feeling a lot better.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:55.17,0:25:56.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道的  我一直在\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}You know I'm always here for you.
