Dialogue: 0,0:26:02.80,0:26:04.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的确有几年前打斗的痕迹\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}I did see evidence of a struggle there years ago,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:04.76,0:26:06.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但除此之外就没了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}but nothing else.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:06.64,0:26:07.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是说他还活着\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}You mean he's still alive?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:07.85,0:26:09.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有可能  我还在找\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}Possibly. I'm still looking.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:13.44,0:26:15.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘶吼的情况如何  他刚才拿什么打的我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}Where are we on Rip Roar and what did he hit me with?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:15.90,0:26:17.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个叫作聚合炮\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}It's called a Fusion Cannon.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:17.78,0:26:19.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至少一百年后叫这个\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}Or at least it is 100 years from now.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:19.82,0:26:21.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是莱克斯的马拉松激光\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}It's the result of the ingenious combination
