Dialogue: 0,0:26:27.08,0:26:29.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘶吼就是从卫星站偷走了这个\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}That's what Rip Roar stole from the satellite base.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:29.87,0:26:32.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  两种技术结合造就了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}Yes, the combined technologies create an energy beam
Dialogue: 0,0:26:32.42,0:26:35.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超越太阳中心热度100倍的能量束\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}100 times hotter than the center of the sun.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:35.46,0:26:36.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果能造成这样的损坏\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}If it's capable of damage like that,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:36.88,0:26:38.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想想它还能做什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}imagine what else it can do.
