Dialogue: 0,0:26:46.76,0:26:48.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑曜石之北发布就在今天\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}Well, Obsidian North's launch is today.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:48.89,0:26:52.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管安德里亚在计划什么  也许到头了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}So whatever Andrea's been up to, will probably come to a head.
