Dialogue: 0,0:39:18.82,0:39:21.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我这些年确实掌握了一些技能\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}Well, I've developed a few skills over the years.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:23.15,0:39:25.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,过来  我给你准备了礼物\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}Uh, come here. I... I got you something.
