Dialogue: 0,0:39:43.68,0:39:44.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  睁开眼\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}Okay, open.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:47.26,0:39:49.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢德尔XG-1000头盔\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}A Schadel XG-1000.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:49.31,0:39:51.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样我就可以骑摩托车载你了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}So you can be my riding partner.
