Dialogue: 0,0:40:03.74,0:40:04.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:16.46,0:40:17.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别担心\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:17.54,0:40:19.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没有跟安德里亚对质\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}I didn't confront Andrea.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:19.42,0:40:21.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过相信我  我想那么干来着\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}Though, believe me, I wanted to.
