Dialogue: 0,0:40:26.72,0:40:28.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,罗哈斯家族会失去一切\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}if Rip Roar had succeeded.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:29.14,0:40:32.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果他们不是坏蛋  那又会是谁呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}If they're not the villains, then who?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:32.43,0:40:34.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在事情变得更令人难以捉摸了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}And now it gets even more confusing.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:37.06,0:40:41.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超查部抓到了嘶吼  并确认了他的身份\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}The DEO caught Rip Roar and they were able to ID him.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:42.69,0:40:43.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是罗素\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}It's Russell.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:45.61,0:40:46.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}No. What?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:47.16,0:40:48.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这  这不可能\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}That's... That's not possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:51.87,0:40:53.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们不是把他给杀了吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}I thought they killed him.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:53.91,0:40:56.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我做这一切都是为了替他报仇\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}All of this was to avenge his death.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:56.92,0:40:57.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不敢相信\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}I don't believe it.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:57.92,0:41:00.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们是怎么把他变成了那个...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}What could they have done to turn him into that...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:01.71,0:41:02.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怪物\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}monster?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:03.42,0:41:04.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很抱歉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}I'm so sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:06.88,0:41:08.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道这让你很痛苦\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}I know how painful this is.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:09.01,0:41:11.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但现在我们已经拘留了他\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}But now that we have him in custody,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:11.64,0:41:12.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的方面是\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}the good thing is
Dialogue: 0,0:41:12.76,0:41:15.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们终于可以解答你的疑问了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}we can finally get you some answers.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:15.14,0:41:16.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,关于他  安德里亚\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}About him, about Andrea,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:16.43,0:41:19.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以及我们可能发现的其他问题\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}about any other questions we might uncover.
