Dialogue: 0,0:41:24.44,0:41:26.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也知道我不希望你牵涉进来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}You know I didn't want you involved in this.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:27.24,0:41:29.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但如果没有你  我都不知该怎么做到这些\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}But I don't know how I would've done it without you.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:33.83,0:41:34.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}Thank you.
